NOTE: this MIT license covers ONLY the sentrikat-scan client CLI published
on PyPI as the `sentrikat-scan` package. The SentriKat server-side platform
(this repository's main codebase) is licensed under a separate commercial
license — see LICENSE.md at the repository root.

The client CLI is released under a permissive open-source license so that
customers can install it freely on CI runners and developer workstations
without legal friction. It is a connector: it talks to a SentriKat server
instance and requires a valid tenant API key to be useful.
